Privacy Policy for Loans
Thank you for using Loans. This Privacy Policy is to inform you that we do not collect any personal information from our users.

Information We Do Not Collect
Loans does not collect any personal identification information or sensitive data from Users, including but not limited to:

Personal information such as names, email addresses, or contact details.
Device information like IP addresses, device IDs, or operating system details.
Usage data, analytics, or cookies.
Data Security
While we do not collect any user information, we still value the security of your device and data. Loans adopts appropriate data security measures to protect against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction of data.

Children's Privacy
Our App is not intended for children under 10. We do not knowingly collect any information from children under 10. If you believe we have inadvertently collected information from a child, please contact us at qurtas.mail@gmail.com, and we will promptly delete any such data.

Changes to this Privacy Policy
Loans reserves the right to update this Privacy Policy as needed. Any changes to the policy will be reflected with the updated date at the bottom of this page. We encourage Users to check this page occasionally to stay informed about our data practices.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or any concerns related to our app, please contact us at qurtas.mail@gmail.com.
